/ROADMAP.html                           @bo-lora
/TAXONOMY.md                            @bo-lora

/index.html                             @bo-lora
/images/                                @bo-lora


# === Core — load-bearing universal layer ===
# Changes to Core require Core-steward approval. Cross-WG impact —
# every workflow extension imports Core, so Core changes ripple.

/core/                                  @bo-lora
/taxonomy/                              @bo-lora


# === Governance — process and decisions ===
# Changes to governance affect every WG. Owned by the conveners.

/governance/                            @bo-lora
/.github/                               @bo-lora


# === Workflow extensions ===
# Each workflow's directory is owned by its working group. The WG owns
# the spec, the SKOS/OWL/SHACL artifacts, the worked examples, and the
# documentation under its directory. Cross-references INTO the workflow
# from other workflows are not WG-owned (those edges are negotiated).

/clinical-research/                     @bo-lora
